    } catch {}
  });
</script><div aria-roledescription="chat messages" class="relative size-full" data-testid="chat-messages-container" id="scroll-container" role="list" style="contain: strict;"><div class="from-muted to-transparent absolute z-10 transition-opacity pointer-events-none opacity-0 bg-linear-to-t bottom-0 left-0 w-full" style="height: 32px;"></div><div class="from-muted to-transparent absolute z-10 transition-opacity pointer-events-none opacity-100 bg-linear-to-b top-0 left-0 w-full" style="height: 32px;"></div><div class="relative h-full w-full overflow-y-scroll visible-scrollbar @container/messages" id="scroll-inner-container" style="opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; overflow-anchor: none;"><div class="group/message-list mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl text-label-13 leading-relaxed"><div style="overflow-anchor: none; flex: 0 0 auto; position: relative; visibility: hidden; width: 100%; height: 2597.12px;"><div style="position: absolute; width: 100%; left: 0px; top: 0px; visibility: visible;"><div class="flex w-full empty:hidden [&amp;&gt;div]:w-full flex-col py-1.5 px-3 pt-4" style="min-height: auto;"><div id="XJmzYxVX8N8h0zyMMG01vWPJCDLU3uzT" class="@container/message group w-full [&amp;_code]:break-all break-words flex flex-col gap-2 origin-right items-end" data-testid="message" role="listitem" data-touch-active="false" style="transition-property: opacity; transition-duration: 200ms; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.31, 0.1, 0.08, 0.96); transition-delay: 0ms; will-change: auto;"><div class="flex items-end sm:max-w-[min(fit-content,80%)] max-w-[90%] origin-top-right"><div class="border border-v0-gray-200 text-left relative rounded-[16px] px-3 py-1.5 min-w-0 break-words group/message-bubble bg-v0-gray-200" style="transition-property: border-color, background; transition-duration: 300ms; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.31, 0.1, 0.08, 0.96); transition-delay: 0ms; will-change: border-color, background; animation-duration: 0.8s;"><svg width="16" height="16" class="absolute -top-[6px] right-0" fill="var(--v0-gray-200)" style="transition-property: scale, fill; transition-duration: 300ms; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.31, 0.1, 0.08, 0.96); transition-delay: 0ms; will-change: fill;"><path d="M-2.70729e-07 6.19355C8 6.19355 12 4.12903 16 6.99382e-07C16 6.70968 16 13.5 10 16L-2.70729e-07 6.19355Z"></path></svg><div class="prose prose-gray min-w-0 break-words text-label-13 leading-relaxed prose-p:text-label-13 prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-li:text-label-13 prose-li:leading-relaxed prose-code:text-label-13-mono prose-blockquote:text-label-13 prose-blockquote:leading-relaxed w-full"><p>색상 상태 변형 추가 프롬프트 (선택)<br>
대기질 상태별로 4가지 화면 변형을 나란히 보여줘:</p>
<ol>
<li>좋음 — 파랑 테마, PM2.5: 10, PM10: 25</li>
<li>보통 — 초록 테마, PM2.5: 25, PM10: 48</li>
<li>나쁨 — 주황 테마, PM2.5: 55, PM10: 90</li>
<li>매우나쁨 — 빨강 테마, PM2.5: 90, PM10: 140</li>
</ol>
<p>각 변형은 전체 화면을 작은 축척으로 표시하고, 하단에 상태명을 라벨로 표시해줘.</p>
<p>로딩 / 에러 상태 추가 프롬프트 (선택)<br>
같은 화면에 두 가지 추가 상태도 디자인해줘:</p>
<ul>
<li>로딩 상태: PM 수치 영역에 스켈레톤 플레이스홀더를 표시하고, 새로고침 아이콘은 회전 애니메이션 적용. 배경은 회색 중립 계열.</li>
<li>에러 상태: 경고 아이콘과 "데이터를 불러올 수 없습니다" 메시지, "다시 시도" 버튼 표시. 배경은 흐린 회색 계열.</li>
</ul>
<p>모바일 웹 버전으로 만들어줘.</p></div></div></div><div class="relative flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-end pb-1 pt-1.5"><span data-context-pill="true" class="text-[13px] border-v0-alpha-400 group relative max-w-[200px] inline-flex h-[24px] overflow-hidden items-center rounded-[6px] border transition-colors bg-v0-gray-100 [--hover-color:theme(colors.gray.200)] hover:bg-[var(--hover-color)] cursor-pointer"><span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 overflow-hidden h-full !no-underline font-normal pl-1"><div class="relative flex h-4 min-w-4 items-center justify-center [&amp;_svg]:scale-90"><div class="text-v0-gray-900"><svg data-testid="geist-icon" height="16" stroke-linejoin="round" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" style="color: currentcolor;"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M14.5 6.5V13.5C14.5 14.8807 13.3807 16 12 16H4C2.61929 16 1.5 14.8807 1.5 13.5V1.5V0H3H8H9.08579C9.351 0 9.60536 0.105357 9.79289 0.292893L14.2071 4.70711C14.3946 4.89464 14.5 5.149 14.5 5.41421V6.5ZM13 6.5V13.5C13 14.0523 12.5523 14.5 12 14.5H4C3.44772 14.5 3 14.0523 3 13.5V1.5H8V5V6.5H9.5H13ZM9.5 2.12132V5H12.3787L9.5 2.12132Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div><span class="truncate inline overflow-hidden pr-1.5 transition-all" data-state="closed">document.md</span></span></span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-1 justify-end flex-row-reverse mr-[-2px]" style="opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; transform: translateY(0px); transition-property: opacity, transform; transition-duration: 400ms; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.31, 0.1, 0.08, 0.96); transition-delay: 0ms; will-change: transform;"><div class="flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 opacity-0" style="transition-property: opacity; transition-duration: 200ms; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.31, 0.1, 0.08, 0.96); transition-delay: 0ms; will-change: auto;"><button class="focus-visible:ring-offset-background outline-hidden has-focus-visible:ring-2 inline-flex shrink-0