bd]:pr-[6px] relative z-10 size-7 shrink-0 rounded-md px-1 transition-none has-[&gt;svg]:p-0" data-state="closed"><svg data-testid="geist-icon" height="16" stroke-linejoin="round" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; color: currentcolor;"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M6.47141 3.13809L6.94281 2.66669L6 1.72388L5.5286 2.19528L2.19526 5.52861C1.93491 5.78896 1.93491 6.21107 2.19526 6.47142L5.5286 9.80476L6 10.2762L6.94281 9.33335L6.47141 8.86195L4.35948 6.75002H9.66667C10.0497 6.75002 10.429 6.82546 10.7828 6.97204C11.1367 7.11861 11.4582 7.33345 11.7291 7.60429C11.9999 7.87513 12.2147 8.19666 12.3613 8.55053C12.5079 8.90439 12.5833 9.28366 12.5833 9.66669C12.5833 10.0497 12.5079 10.429 12.3613 10.7828C12.2147 11.1367 11.9999 11.4582 11.7291 11.7291C11.4582 11.9999 11.1367 12.2148 10.7828 12.3613C10.429 12.5079 10.0497 12.5834 9.66667 12.5834H7.33333H6.58333V14.0834H7.33333H9.66667C10.2467 14.0834 10.821 13.9691 11.3569 13.7472C11.8927 13.5252 12.3796 13.1999 12.7897 12.7897C13.1998 12.3796 13.5252 11.8927 13.7471 11.3569C13.9691 10.821 14.0833 10.2467 14.0833 9.66669C14.0833 9.08668 13.9691 8.51235 13.7471 7.9765C13.5252 7.44065 13.1998 6.95376 12.7897 6.54363C12.3796 6.13351 11.8927 5.80818 11.3569 5.58622C10.821 5.36426 10.2467 5.25002 9.66667 5.25002H4.35948L6.47141 3.13809Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><span class="sr-only">Restore</span></button></div></div></div><div data-state="closed" id="radix-_r_4l_" hidden="" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-_r_4k_" data-orientation="vertical" class="primitives-module__gWXxya__content" style="--radix-accordion-content-height: var(--radix-collapsible-content-height); --radix-accordion-content-width: var(--radix-collapsible-content-width);"></div></div></div></div></div></div><p data-seg="_r_4o_"><span data-seg="_r_4p_">DustNow 대기질 앱의 상태별 쇼케이스를 완성했습니다!</span></p><p data-seg="_r_4r_"><strong data-seg="_r_4s_"><span data-seg="_r_4t_">구현 내용:</span></strong></p><ul data-seg="_r_4v_"><li data-seg="_r_50_"><strong data-seg="_r_51_"><span data-seg="_r_52_">4가지 대기질 상태</span></strong><span data-seg="_r_54_">: 좋음(파랑), 보통(초록), 나쁨(주황), 매우나쁨(빨강) - 각각 지정된 PM2.5/PM10 수치로 표시</span></li><li data-seg="_r_56_"><strong data-seg="_r_57_"><span data-seg="_r_58_">로딩 상태</span></strong><span data-seg="_r_5a_">: 스켈레톤 플레이스홀더와 회전하는 새로고침 아이콘, 회색 배경</span></li><li data-seg="_r_5c_"><strong data-seg="_r_5d_"><span data-seg="_r_5e_">에러 상태</span></strong><span data-seg="_r_5g_">: 경고 아이콘, "데이터를 불러올 수 없습니다" 메시지, "다시 시도" 버튼</span></li></ul><p data-seg="_r_5i_"><span data-seg="_r_5j_">각 변형은 모바일 폰 프레임 안에 축소된 전체 화면으로 표시되며, 하단에 상태명 라벨이 있습니다. 반응형 그리드로 모바일에서는 2열, 태블릿에서는 3열, 데스크톱에서는 6열로 표시됩니다.</span></p></div></div><div class="min-w-0 w-full"><div data-rich-task="true" class="w-full" data-orientation="vertical"><div style="opacity: 1;"><div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-_r_5m_" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-_r_5l_" class="group/trigger w-full flex items-center gap-2 text-v0-gray-900 rounded-[6px] min-h-6 truncate min-w-0 focus-visible:ring-offset-background outline-hidden has-focus-visible:ring-2 ring-v0-blue-700 transition focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-1 cursor-pointer" tabindex="0" data-radix-collection-item=""><span class="place-items-center place-content-center grid [&amp;&gt;*]:grid-stack [&amp;_svg]:size-[13px] text-v0-gray-700 min-w-[13px] min-h-[13px] group-hover/trigger:text-v0-gray-900 group-focus-visible/trigger:text-v0-gray-900" style="transition-property: color; transition-duration: 150ms; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.31, 0.1, 0.08, 0.96); transition-delay: 0ms; will-change: color;"><span class="group-hover/trigger:opacity-0 group-hover/trigger:scale-80 opacity-100 scale-100 group-data-[state=open]/trigger:opacity-0 group-data-[state=open]/trigger:scale-80 group-focus-visible/trigger: